    "title": "SeaKing Bait Board B04 (830mm x 430mm) & 2 Game Rated Rod Holders",
    "body_html": "<div data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"ProductItem-details-excerpt\" data-content-field=\"excerpt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Sea King B04</span><b></b></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The SeaKing SK-B04 offers the same robust features as our classic B01 and B03 models, now </span><span>enhanced with integrated moulded cup holders for added convenience. Designed for those who </span><span>appreciate functionality with a touch of luxury, the SK-B04 ensures you have everything you need for </span><span>a successful fishing trip, combined with the practicality of built-in cup holders for added comfort on the </span><span>water.</span><strong></strong></p>\n</div>",
